🕒 Digital Clock

A simple Digital Clock application that displays the current time in HH:MM:SS format and updates every second.


_________________________________________

📌 Features

Real-time clock updates.

12-hour and 24-hour format support.

Displays hours, minutes, and seconds.



_________________________________________

💻 TECHNOLOGY USED

language used -- C programming languages 

complier the program using vs studio code or any c compiler website 



